ghost-role-information-listeningop-name = Syndicate Listening Post Operative
ghost-role-information-listeningop-description = You are a Listening Post operative. Tap into station communications, contact and assist syndicate operatives (if any), and use your tools to spread false information and syndicate propaganda.
ghost-role-information-listeningop-rules = You are a [color=red][bold]Team Antagonist[/bold][/color] with all other Syndicate agents.
                                           Make sure your outpost doesn't fall into enemy hands and [bold]do not abandon the outpost[/bold] under any circumstances.

                                           You don't remember any of your previous life, and you don't remember anything you learned as a ghost.
